# Before commit or push

Do not run `git commit` or `git push` until the working tree is verified clean from the repo root:

1. `npm run verify` (runs `typecheck`, ESLint, and `vitest run`)

If any step fails, fix the issues first, then re-run `npm run verify`.

Do not treat editor-only diagnostics as sufficient; use the same commands CI or teammates would run.

See `AGENTS.md` for the same policy in-repo.
